To offer full functionality, the clustering tool needs the following libraries
to be installed on your system

* Muster clustering library

http://tgamblin.github.com/muster/main.html

* Computational Geometry Algorithms Library (CGAL)

http://www.cgal.org/

* GNU MPFR (needed by CGAL)

http://www.mpfr.org/

* The GNU Multiple Precision Arithmetic Library (needed by CGAL)

http://www.gmplib.org

* Boost headers and Boost thread libraries (needed by Muster and CGAL)

http://www.boost.org/

* An MPI implementation.

The suite has been tested using MPICH

http://www.mcs.anl.gov/research/projects/mpich2/

* The SeqAn library for multiple sequence analysis

http://www.seqan.de/

* libMRNetApp

Also available in the BSC Tools group

